# Livewire publishes JS assets here. Tracking them causes drift bugs whenever
# the composer-installed Livewire version moves ahead — the browser ends up
# running stale JS against newer server PHP. Let Livewire's controller serve
# the matching version via /livewire/livewire.js instead.
/public/vendor/livewire

